Bug ID:007
Title: 7.After adding a new location it is not shown on the Home Page
Description: Adding a new location is not shown on the Home Page but is shown on the Locations,Reservations and Update Price pages.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on Add a location in the navbar.
Step 4 : Fill in the fields with correct data.
Step 5 : Click the Add location button.
Step 6 : Affirm the "You have successfully added a location" message.
Step 7 : Go to the Home Page again (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 8 : Affirm your new location is not seen with the locations added from the admins.



Expected Result:
After adding a new location your new location should be added to the Home Page with the rest.

Actual Result:
After adding your new location it is not shown on the Home Page but it is shown everywhere else.

Severity:
High  

Priority:
High

Additional Information:
When adding a new location you should have the ability to upload an image like the rest of the locations that are added before.

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
